Package oop2.jeopardy.game

Class QuestionBank

java.lang.Object
oop2.jeopardy.game.QuestionBank
public class QuestionBank extends Object
Stores and organizes all questions for the game. Provides quick access to questions by category and value, as well as utility methods for retrieving lists and counts.

Used by GameBoard and Game to fetch questions and populate the game board.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Kadie Bisnath - 816036090
